* Kaggle

"The most prominent data analysis platform is Australian-based Kaggle, which recently raised $11 million in
funding. Kaggle uses the mechanics of a competition platform and sets up predictive modelling challenges
for its crowd of data scientists, many of them academics.


* In October 2006 Netflix offered a $1 million prize to whoever could improve their video recommendation algorithm by
10%. The final prize was awarded in October 2009 to a team which combined two of the previous top-performing teams."


